rows.label: qst105606_msg001
rows.name: The objective has been achieved.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0001
rows.name: We've cleaned up over here!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0002
rows.name: Your Highness! I am glad you are safe.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0003
rows.name:
We have also secured the
rebel soldiers here.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0004
rows.name:
Damn it! The one who should be
judged is not us, but the King
who deceived the people!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0005
rows.name:
Doesn't anyone feel the
same!? He is not of the
hero Adel-sama's bloodline!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0006
rows.name:
Now is the time to rise up and strike
down the royal family that has deceived
us for hundreds of years...!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0007
rows.name:
That's enough... I don't want
to have to stop you by force.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0008
rows.name:
Hmph! What does the prodigal
prince who's been wandering
for years have to say!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0009
rows.name:
We are the victims!
Yes, look at the city!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0010
rows.name:
The hungry, the freezing...
This is the result of being
ruled by a false lineage!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0011
rows.name: I told you to shut up!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0012
rows.name:
I understand what you're sayin'.
I'm one of the deceived, too.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0013
rows.name:
But the state of Luxuria now... the
state of the capital Teos Aure... has
nothin' to do with Adel's blood!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0014
rows.name:
It's not too late to judge
me and my old man after
we've rebuilt Luxuria.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0015
rows.name: Prince...

rows.label: qst105606_msg0016
rows.name: ...Hah! Thanks for the sermon.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0017
rows.name:
It's about time... The
objective has been achieved.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0018
rows.name:
You royals will be killed at the
hands of Adel-sama! Ahahahaha!!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0019
rows.name: At Adel's hands...? What do you mean?!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0020
rows.name: Like I'd tell you...! Hahahaha!!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0021
rows.name:
This is gettin' nowhere... You
there, take care of this guy!
Make him spill everything.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0022
rows.name: Yes, sir! Leave it to me!!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0023
rows.name:
They were our comrades
once. Go easy on them.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0024
rows.name: Yes, sir!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0025
rows.name: Prince! Let's look for the key!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0026
rows.name:
Yeah... That weird thing he
said is botherin' me, but...
